/* A20OS Native ABI syscall table definition (X-macro pattern). */
/* NOTE: This file is intentionally NOT include-guarded because it uses the
 * X-macro pattern and must be included multiple times with different
 * A20_NATIVE_SYSCALL macro definitions active. */

